{"tid":1058802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"情到濃時吞下男友精液　女嚴重過敏休克險死","createTime":"2019-03-12T19:46:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T04:27:46.000Z","uid":234553,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"68f1bb7f1b163f1adff969bffaab188724acb966","tid":1058802,"uid":234553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T19:46:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190313/640_749e6079c16686b5d8af856c11bf52a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190313%2F640_749e6079c16686b5d8af856c11bf52a0.jpg&h=f478c652&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n西班牙一名女子，替男友口交後吞下精液，導致過敏性休克，差點死亡。<br />\n<br />\n隨著科技日新月異，醫療技術大幅度提升，現代人面對的「過敏」案例卻也越來越多，有專家認為，就是因為從小成長的環境「太過乾淨」，同時又吃了太多加工食品，才會有層出不窮的「過敏」個案。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最新一期的《英國醫學期刊》(BMJ，British Medical Journal)刊載了一起罕見案例，西班牙阿利坎特(Alicante)一名31歲女子，日前和大她1歲的男友恩愛時，吞下了男友的精液，沒多久她開始嘔吐，接著呼吸困難，全身還發出疹子，並失去意識，男友連忙帶她就醫，醫師初步診斷，她是「過敏性休克」(anaphylactic shock)，在緊急替她使用腎上腺素(adrenaline)、類固醇(steroids)與氣管擴張劑沙丁胺醇(salbutamol)後，她才順利恢復呼吸，住院一周後康復出院。<br />\n<br />\n這名女子曾對盤尼西林類的抗生素過敏，但她很確定，發病前並沒有接觸任何這類的藥物。阿利坎特大學綜合醫院(Hospital General Universitari d'Alacant)醫師亞曼娜拉(Susana Almenara)，發現女子男友當時因為內耳發炎，正在服用含有阿莫西林-克拉維酸(amoxicillin-clavulanic acid)的抗菌藥物，這才證實，誘發女子過敏的原因是「藉由精液傳遞的阿莫西林」(seminal transfer of amoxicillin)。《英國醫學期刊》相信，這應該是文獻紀載的首起案例。<br />\n<br />\n亞曼娜拉呼籲任何曾有藥物過敏症狀的女性，在從事可能接觸、攝入對方體液的性行為，包括口交時，為了個人安全，務必全程使用保險套，「因為性交、接吻過程中的體液交換，導致藥物過敏的案例早有紀載」，「這起案例讓我們知道，口交也會有相對的危險性」，「過敏性休克的處置，正確的早期診斷才能給予充足的治療，以減少傷亡」。（於慶中／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190313/1531998/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190313%2F1531998%2F&d=fcvOs274DMK6OEArnk0La%2F3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=45df43f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190313%2F1531998%2F&h=69a395a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190313/1531998/</a>"},{"pid":"d83f1d80061fdd77e549c16a84e2504468ac235d","tid":1058802,"uid":294,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T19:47:25.000Z","msg":"破事兒"},{"pid":"f01e6c388d7af8ce376e08ee5a9718f32d805415","tid":1058802,"uid":100347,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T20:44:38.000Z","msg":"試過中出條女 佢皮膚敏感 難道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2c1d837e21efba40a963d8524b6c6f71d29ed3d","tid":1058802,"uid":9681,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T20:53:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><blockquote>發現女子男友當時因為內耳發炎，正在服用含有阿莫西林-克拉維酸(amoxicillin-clavulanic acid)的抗菌藥物，這才證實，誘發女子過敏的原因是「藉由精液傳遞的阿莫西林」(seminal transfer of amoxicillin)。</blockquote></span><br />\n<br />\n食咩射咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8822069892f6ab9c4e16b5d0706c0bb6f13da9fa","tid":1058802,"uid":59743,"like":86,"dislike":3,"score":83,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T20:53:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YvzS9ee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYvzS9ee.jpg&h=f3ca322a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"69b4eccaeea2048585eb699b194923d2ef79c941","tid":1058802,"uid":90704,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T22:36:55.000Z","msg":"毒撚啲精都敢吞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65dea879c2641d5f9a030506ee8f457667430f10","tid":1058802,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T22:38:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3ad0d5